| Field | TLV | Length | Value | Description |
|-------|-----|--------|-------|-------------|
| **msglen** | `01 82 01 2A` | `82 01 2A` (298 bytes) | 298 bytes | Total message length |
| **headerlen** | `02 82 00 64` | `82 00 64` (100 bytes) | 100 bytes | Header length |
| **timestamp** | `03 11 32 30 32 36 2D 30 37 2D 30 37 20 31 34 3A 33 32 3A 31 35` | `11` (17 bytes) | `2026-07-07 14:32:15` | CP timestamp |
| **user** | `04 08 4C 4E 58 54 4F 4F 4C 32` | `08` (8 bytes) | `LNXTOOL2` | Linux guest |
| **os_user** | `05 08 6C 6E 78 61 64 6D 69 6E` | `08` (8 bytes) | `lnxadmin` | OS username |
| **pid** | `06 02 30 39` | `02` (2 bytes) | `39` (hex) = `12345` (dec) | Process ID |
| **msg_part** | `07 01 31` | `01` (1 byte) | `1` | Message part (1/n) |
| **req_type** | `08 01 30` | `01` (1 byte) | `0` | Request type (text-only) |
